3:39 Weapons
5:38 Techs and Tips

https://www.reddit.com/r/Genshin_Impact/comments/nuv0f7/amber_solo_1231_in_218/

Amber Mains Master Doc:
https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_Xrpd-uTQsthisSlAd1f4KM5I5kyz6idDYK1Kct7w3I/edit

I'm not really sure what to put here, so here's a bunch of clickbait taglines:
AMBER IS INSANE! BEST SUPPORT IN THE GAME! THIS CHANGES EVERYTHING! BEST PHYSICAL DPS IN THE GAME??? EVERYONE IS SLEEPING ON THIS UNIT!

Amber is a free to play pyro bow character in Genshin Impact and she's just cute enough that you should play her in the newest Genshin Impact 1.6 Update. Make sure to learn how to build her as a pyro dps, physical dps, and pyro support!
